Package: pixels
Type: Package
Title: Realtime and Interactive Voxels
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Javier", "Luraschi", email = "javier@rstudio.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Maintainer: Javier Luraschi <javier@rstudio.com>
Description: Provides tools to show and draw image voxels using 'HTML' widgets 
  and 'Shiny' applications.  It can be used to visualize spatial datasets or
  'Minecrafts' like worlds.
